---
---

<section class="v2-about" id="v2-sobre">
  <div class="v2-container">
    <div class="v2-about-grid">
      <div class="v2-about-img v2-reveal">
        <div class="v2-img-frame">
          <img src="/images/sobre-nos.png" alt="Equipe Regê Engenharia" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="v2-about-badge-float">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m2 22 9.6-9.6"/><path d="m17 7-2.5 2.5"/><path d="M14.5 2 22 9.5l-7 7L7.5 9l7-7z"/></svg>
          <div>
            <strong>Chave na Mão</strong>
            <span>Processo 100% gerenciado</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="v2-about-text v2-reveal v2-reveal-delay-1">
        <span class="v2-eyebrow">QUEM SOMOS</span>
        <h2 class="v2-section-title">Engenharia com<br /><em>propósito real.</em></h2>
        <div class="v2-title-underline"></div>
        <p class="v2-about-lead">A Regê Engenharia nasceu com o objetivo de materializar projetos de forma transparente, técnica e sofisticada.</p>
        <p class="v2-about-body">Com sede em Navegantes - SC, somos especializados no gerenciamento de obras residenciais e comerciais no modelo <strong>chave na mão (turnkey)</strong>. Cuidamos de cada etapa do processo construtivo: desde os estudos preliminares, modelagem de projetos integrados, orçamento executivo detalhado até a execução técnica no canteiro e a entrega das chaves.</p>
        <div class="v2-pillars">
          <div class="v2-pillar">
            <div class="v2-pillar-icon">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div><h4>Transparência</h4><p>Relatórios financeiros claros e controle rígido.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="v2-pillar">
            <div class="v2-pillar-icon">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"/><path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div><h4>Qualidade</h4><p>Materiais certificados e mão de obra qualificada.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="v2-pillar">
            <div class="v2-pillar-icon">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div><h4>Pontualidade</h4><p>Cumprimento rigoroso dos prazos acordados.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="v2-pillar">
            <div class="v2-pillar-icon">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div><h4>Dedicação</h4><p>Atendimento personalizado e próximo ao cliente.</p></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
/* ABOUT */
.v2-about {
  padding: 8rem 0;
  background: var(--v2-white);
  position: relative;
}
.v2-about::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 3px;
  background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--v2-gold), transparent);
}
.v2-about-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.1fr;
  gap: 6rem;
  align-items: center;
}
.v2-about-img { position: relative; }
.v2-img-frame {
  position: relative;
  aspect-ratio: 4/5;
  border-radius: var(--v2-radius-lg);
  overflow: hidden;
  box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(8,14,23,0.2);
}
.v2-img-frame img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  transition: transform 0.8s var(--v2-ease);
}
.v2-img-frame:hover img { transform: scale(1.04); }
.v2-img-frame::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent 60%, rgba(8,14,23,0.4));
  z-index: 1;
  pointer-events: none;
}
.v2-about-badge-float {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -1.5rem;
  right: -1.5rem;
  background: var(--v2-dark);
  color: var(--v2-white);
  padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
  border-radius: var(--v2-radius);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 1rem;
  box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(8,14,23,0.3);
  border: 1px solid var(--v2-border);
  z-index: 2;
}
.v2-about-badge-float svg { stroke: var(--v2-gold); flex-shrink: 0; }
.v2-about-badge-float strong {
  display: block;
  font-family: var(--v2-font-display);
  font-size: 0.78rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  color: var(--v2-white);
}
.v2-about-badge-float span {
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  color: var(--v2-muted);
  display: block;
  margin-top: 0.1rem;
}
.v2-about-text { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
.v2-title-underline {
  width: 50px;
  height: 3px;
  background: var(--v2-gold);
  margin: 1.5rem 0 2rem;
  border-radius: 2px;
}
.v2-about-lead {
  font-family: var(--v2-font-serif);
  font-style: italic;
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  color: var(--v2-dark-3);
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}
.v2-about-body {
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  color: #555;
  line-height: 1.9;
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
}
.v2-about-body strong { color: var(--v2-dark); font-weight: 700; }
.v2-pillars {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(8,14,23,0.08);
  padding-top: 2rem;
}
.v2-pillar { display: flex; gap: 0.85rem; }
.v2-pillar-icon {
  width: 38px;
  height: 38px;
  background: var(--v2-gold-muted);
  border-radius: var(--v2-radius);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
}
.v2-pillar-icon svg { stroke: var(--v2-gold); }
.v2-pillar h4 {
  font-family: var(--v2-font-display);
  font-size: 0.78rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--v2-dark);
  margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
}
.v2-pillar p { font-size: 0.82rem; color: #666; line-height: 1.5; }

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .v2-about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
  .v2-about-img { order: -1; }
  .v2-img-frame { aspect-ratio: 16/9; max-height: 400px; }
  .v2-about-badge-float { bottom: -1rem; right: 0.5rem; }
  .v2-pillars { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.25rem; }
}
</style>
